    "en": "HORDI recommendation for brinjal / eggplant (Solanum melongena) up to 1300 m elevation. Well-drained soil at pH 5.5–5.8. Spacing 90 × 60 cm, seed rate 350 g/ha. Three-stage fertilizer. First harvest 10–12 weeks after transplanting; 7-day picking intervals; OPV 18–20 t/ha, hybrids 30–40 t/ha."
